# Agent coordination

When working on LOCUS Production Spec (plan locus_final_production_spec_v3):

1. **Before starting:** read `.cursor/plans/AGENT_COORDINATION.md` and the relevant `stage-N-*.plan.md`.
2. **Scope:** change only files in your assigned zone. Do not modify other agents' files.
3. **After completion:** update the stage status in AGENT_COORDINATION.md (⬜ → ✅).

If the user says "работай по этапу N" or "work on stage N", use `.cursor/plans/stage-N-*.plan.md` as the task list.
